@frontName = me-front.jpg
@frontPath = ../assets/{{frontName}}
@frontType = image/jpeg

@backName = me-back.jpg
@backPath= ../assets/{{backName}}
@backType = image/jpeg

### JOB_REQUEST

POST http://localhost:8000/extract HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary{{$timestamp}}

------WebKitFormBoundary{{$timestamp}}
content-disposition: form-data; name="front"; filename="{{frontName}}"
Content-Type: {{frontType}}

< {{frontPath}}

------WebKitFormBoundary{{$timestamp}}
content-disposition: form-data; name="back"; filename="{{backName}}"
Content-Type: {{backType}}

< {{backPath}}


------WebKitFormBoundary{{$timestamp}}--


### 

GET http://localhost:8000{{JOB_REQUEST.response.body.status_url}} HTTP/1.1
